games.farhaduneci.com
====================

A collection of browser-based games and HTML experiments by Farhad Uneci.

Hosted on Cloudflare Workers at https://games.farhaduneci.com


Structure
---------

  public/             Static assets served by Cloudflare
    index.html        Games listing page (the homepage)
    styles.css        Compiled Tailwind CSS (do not edit directly)
    html/             Individual game files — one HTML per game

  src/
    input.css         Tailwind v4 source (compiled to public/styles.css)

  wrangler.jsonc      Cloudflare Workers config
  package.json        Dev dependencies (Tailwind, Wrangler)


Development
-----------

  npm install
  npx wrangler dev          # local preview at http://localhost:8787
  npx wrangler deploy       # deploy to Cloudflare


Adding a game
-------------

1. Put the standalone HTML file in public/html/
2. Add an entry for it in public/index.html (games array in the inline script)
3. Deploy


Tech
----

  - Cloudflare Workers (static assets mode)
  - Tailwind CSS v4
  - Vanilla HTML/JS — no framework


